data.description: NO HOA! NEW HVAC installed August 2023. Welcome to this spacious home with a fantastic bonus - an above ground pool installed in 2020 and a full bathroom and extra room downstairs! This home offers ample space for your family's needs. As you walk up to the home you will notice the large and inviting front porch with a large driveway. The main floor includes the kitchen, formal living room, family room with a fireplace and built in shelves, dining room, breakfast nook, laundry room, half guest bathroom, full bathroom and a 5th bedroom that would be perfect for an office, bedroom or guest room! The kitchen has stainless steel appliances, nice backsplash and granite countertops. Upstairs, you'll find four additional bedrooms, including the master bedroom. Newer carpet in most of the homeThis home is perfect for accommodating guests or for a growing family. Step outside to the backyard, where you'll discover a private haven featuring a refreshing pool, privacy fence, a covered screened in porch for outdoor dining, a 10x10 shed, 12x10 single car garage shed and storage closet off the porch. The pool is 15x26, 4.6ft deep salt water pool installed in 2020 with a robotic auto cleaner. The dining room is being used as a workout area. All you have to do is enjoy life in this great neighborhood with less than a 10 minute commute to Historic Downtown Summerville where the Town of Summerville hosts plenty of events with easy access and short distance to Gahagan Park, plenty of shopping, restaurants, walking & bike trails, I-26, Nexton and a short commute to the Walmart warehouse, Volvo plant, and still easy access to Boeing, Airport, Bosch, Hospitals and less than a 25 minute commute to Historic Downtown Charleston. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your place to call home! If schools and square footage are important, please verify.
